videos.description: Oklahoma State RB Justice Hill runs up the sideline past Texas' defense and into the end zone for a 30-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State RB Hill breaks free for 30-yard TD

videos.description: Oklahoma State WR James Washington extends the Cowboys' lead over Texas by breaking a tackle and racing 54 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State receiver evades tackles, breaks free for score

videos.description: Shane Buechele pass complete to Dorian Leonard for 49 yds to the OKSt 2 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: S. Buechele pass,to D. Leonard for 49 yds to Oklahoma State's 1 yard line

videos.description: Texas RB D'Onta Foreman rushes straight through Oklahoma State's defense for a 22-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas RB Foreman runs up the gut for 22-yard TD

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Trey Carter blocks Texas' extra point, collects the ball and starts running downfield. Carter then laterals to Tre Flowers, who finishes the run for two points.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State blocks extra point, uses lateral to score

videos.description: Texas QB Tyrone Swoopes uses his strength to shed a tackle on his way to the end zone, giving the Longhorns the lead over Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Swoopes runs through Oklahoma State defenders for score

videos.description: Oklahoma State QB Mason Rudolph runs 10 yards and dives into the end zone for the touchdown, giving the Cowboys the lead back over Texas.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State QB Rudolph dives into end zone for score

videos.description: Texas QB Shane Buechele finds Andrew Beck open over the middle for a 42-yard touchdown pass, giving the Longhorns the lead back from Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Buechele finds wide-open Beck for 42-yard TD

videos.description: Mason Rudolph pass complete to Jhajuan Seales for 34 yds to the Texas 36 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: M. Rudolph pass,to J. Seales for 34 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Oklahoma State QB Mason Rudolph fires a laser to Jalen McCleskey for a 36-yard touchdown pass, which gives the Cowboys the lead back over Texas.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State retakes lead with 36-yard TD pass

videos.description: Oklahoma State WR Jalen McCleskey showcases his athleticism breaking out of a tackle and scoring a 52-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State WR McCleskey sheds tackle for 52-yard TD

videos.description: Barry Sanders run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: B. Sanders run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.description: Texas RB D'Onta Foreman races through Oklahoma State's defensive line and scores a 62-yard touchdown to keep the Longhorns within striking distance of the Cowboys.
videos.headline: Texas RB Foreman finds big hole for 62-yard TD

videos.description: Texas RB D'Onta Foreman has to be helped off the field due to a lower-body injury and does not return to the game against Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Texas RB Foreman leaves game with lower-body injury
